<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Affected File: Zend/Controller/Action/Helper/Url.php</p>

<p>The returned url from the simple method should have an "/" as prefix, that dynamic created url`s will be redirected correct by the browser.</p>

<p>An possible patch could be:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
--- Url.php     2007-09-05 14:39:14.404473800 +0200
+++ Url.php  2007-09-06 21:53:02.218750000 +0200
@@ -73,6 +73,8 @@
             $url .= '/' . $paramString;
         }

+        $url = '/' . ltrim($url, '/');
+
         return $url;
     }
</code></pre>

